ut let us go for the three-peat.\\\"\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other boys\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"the three-peat\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain had rested individual finalists Scott and Richards for the morning heats and still qualified fastest for the evening's final to confirm their status as heavy favourites.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1514, \"end\": 1521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9589204828858098, \"rank\": 0.042839332010513306, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 1554, \"end\": 1559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.9995858716655791, \"rank\": 0.0004142978223624617, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"individual finalists\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning heats\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"their status\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy favourites\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans, however, stuck within half-a-second at every changeover before a devastating final leg from anchorman Scott finally saw Britain pull clear.\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1693, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.084486816543949e-22, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp